    "This criterion ensures alignment with the research questions and objectives.",
    "• Empirical Research: Studies involving practical experiments or empirical evaluations using specific datasets were prioritized to emphasize evidence-based findings.",
    "• Comprehensive Evaluation: Each chosen study must provide a detailed evaluation of the performance, opportunities, and challenges of LLMs in education.• Source Quality: The scope was limited to reputable journals, conferences, or books to ensure reliability and scholarly rigor.",
    "Table 4 Search string formulation Keyword Synonym/Alternative word Education (\"program\" OR \"system\") ChatGpt (\"AI\" OR \"ML\") Application (\"metrics\" OR \"classification\") Methods (\"Techniques\" OR \"Framework\") Vol.",
    ":(0123456789) Discover Sustainability (2025) 6:27 | https://doi.org/10.1007/s43621-025-00815-8 Review Exclusion criteriaStudies meeting the following criteria were excluded from the review:• Published Before 2018: Older studies were excluded to limit the scope to recent developments, given the rapid evolution of LLM technology."
